The Gen Abubakar Abdulsalam’s peace committee met with INEC chair and security chiefs ahead of the 2019 general elections. The meeting according to Abdulsalam is to sue for peace as the polity is already heated up. The committee therefore appealed to all stakeholders to follow the part of peace. It will also meet with the 91 registered political parties later today. The committee will be briefing newsmen after the meeting with the political parties.  Details later… 